title: Blur-Parklife [1994]
description:
Parklife is the third album by English alternative rock band Blur released on 25 April 1994.
 After disappointing sales for their previous album Modern Life is Rubbish (1993), 
Parklife established Blur in the UK, helped by its four hit singles: "Girls & Boys", 
"End of a Century", "Parklife" and "To the End". The album was certified quadruple platinum in the UK.
 Although the album failed to chart in the United States, "Girls & Boys" became a minor hit there.
